OL,3,CSexual abuse survivor says new scheme
OL,4,Cis building 'compassionate bridges'
OL,6,F"It was very scary," she said.
OL,8,F"I just remember there being a lot of
OL,9,Fmale officers.
OL,11,F"And I was just asked a lot of
OL,12,Fquestions and there was a lot of
OL,13,Fwriting involved. My memories are that
OL,14,FI was very overwhelmed and I was very
OL,15,Ffrightened."
OL,17,FThe scheme, called FIDES, has been
OL,18,Flaunched by Sussex Police.
