OL,3,CSexual abuse survivor says new scheme
OL,4,Cis building 'compassionate bridges'
OL,6,FIt comes 18 months after ITV News
OL,7,FMeridian revealed that only 3% of
OL,8,FSussex Police investigations into
OL,9,Fsexual offences resulted in a
OL,10,Fprosecution.
OL,12,FEight new Victim Support Co-ordinators
OL,13,Fwill act as a single point of contact
OL,14,Ffor survivors, build a rapport with
OL,15,Fthem and help to develop an
OL,16,Funderstanding of what barriers exist
OL,17,Fin reporting and where possible
OL,18,Fsupport a prosecution.
