OL,3,CSexual abuse survivor says new scheme
OL,4,Cis building 'compassionate bridges'
OL,6,FMichelle, who now volunteers with
OL,7,FSurvivors Network says she hopes the
OL,8,Fservice will continue to build
OL,9,Fcompassionate bridges with courageous
OL,10,Fsouls who reach out for help and
OL,11,Freport.
OL,13,F"People need to be able to walk into
OL,14,Fan environment where they feel safe
OL,15,Fand they feel heard and they are
OL,16,Fsupported all the way through," she
OL,17,Fadded.
