OL,3,CSexual abuse survivor says new scheme
OL,4,Cis building 'compassionate bridges'
OL,6,F"It's important that we have this
OL,7,Fcontinued growth and understanding
OL,8,Fthat people need to be heard in a very
OL,9,Fgentle and calm space, where they feel
OL,10,Fsafe."
OL,12,FThe aim of Victim Support Co-
OL,13,Fordinators is to alleviate the volume
OL,14,Fof cases currently held by specialist
OL,15,Frape investigation officers so they
OL,16,Fcan concentrate on achieving
OL,17,Fprosecutions, develop trust and
OL,18,Fconfidence with victims and,
OL,19,Fultimately, to support an increase in
OL,20,Fpositive outcomes and improved
OL,21,Fconviction rates.
